5. Operating Cash Flow Ratio

6. Return on Equity (ROE)

   - ROE = 112,375.10 / 16,056,187.55 = 0.007 = 0.7%

7. Accounts Receivable Turnover Ratio

   - Average Accounts Receivable = (0 + 321,015.98) / 2 = 160,507.99
   - Accounts Receivable Turnover Ratio = 775,598.77 / 160,507.99 = 4.831
